                        "Microsoft Zira Desktop - English (United States)-English Speech - Screen Reader.Muted": 0,
                        "Microsoft Zira Desktop - English (United States)-English Speech - Screen Reader.Voice": 0,
                        "Microsoft Zira Desktop - English (United States)-English Speech - Screen Reader.Rate": 110,
                        "Microsoft Zira Desktop - English (United States)-English Speech - Screen Reader.Volume": 90,
                        "Microsoft Zira Desktop - English (United States)-English Speech - Screen Reader.Pitch": 40,

                        // [Microsoft Zira Desktop - English (United States)-English Speech - DocReader]
